transcript:
Customer: Hello

Executive: Hello
Customer: Haan ji sir namaskar.
Executive: Namaskar sir kaise hain aap?
Customer: Ji sir badhiya.
Executive: Param se baat kar raha tha IndiaMART se.
Customer: Achcha ji ji ji ji sir ji ji. Wo wo certificate aa gaya?
Executive: Mil gaya kya?
Executive: Nahi sir abhi nahi mila hai.
Customer: Aapne tracking track kiya jo tracking ID maine diya tha aapko?
Executive: Nahi sir maine tracking bhi nahi kiya.
Executive: Ek bar wo meeting wala lag utna adhura rah gaya tha to ye profile pending pada hua hai sir ek bar kar lenge ek bar 10 minute ke liye free ho abhi.
Customer: Haan ji thik hai sir.
Executive: Thik hai haan ji main free hu abhi.
Customer: Ji.
Executive: Main bhej raha hu kyuki us din aapne chhod diya tha na to fir pura nahi ho paya tha.
Customer: Haan ji haan ji ji ji.
Executive: Thik hai sir maine bheja ek maine bheja ek bar aap join karo.
Customer: Ji ji.
Executive: Bas.
Executive: Maine bhej diya ek bar aap dekho aapki email ID.
Customer: Ji dekh raha hu.

[inaudible]
